":{"id":"20260305082130-4noyso8","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"构造函数可以有多个，也可以不定义，支持重载；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-wzsu5nd","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-wzsu5nd","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-ll80k59","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ll80k59","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"函数名与类名相同，无返回类型，智只能自动调用；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-u8u5shx","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-u8u5shx","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-wyentzm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-wyentzm","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"并\u003cfont color=\"#c0504d\"\u003e不负责申请对象本身的空间\u003c/font\u003e，只做空间的初始化操作，或申请体外空间。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-eqreahg","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-eqreahg","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.2 初始化"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-m4bjkcg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-m4bjkcg","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"初始化分为\u003cfont color=\"#d83931\"\u003e在构造函数体前初始化\u003c/font\u003e与\u003cfont color=\"#d83931\"\u003e在构造函数体中初始化\u003c/font\u003e，还有\u003cfont color=\"#d83931\"\u003e定义时赋值\u003c/font\u003e（其原理和赋值流程等于在构造函数体前初始化）。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-fxdxbdp","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-fxdxbdp","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"ClassName::ClassName(parameter1, parameter2, argument_for_member1, arg1...)\n    : member1(argument_for_member1),\n      member2(argument_for_member2),\n      classmenber(arg1, arg2, ...)\n      // 在构造函数体前初始化\n{\n    // 在构造函数体中初始化：这里可以执行其他逻辑，但不能再初始化上述成员\n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-8n7yr4v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-8n7yr4v","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\u003cfont color=\"#d83931\"\u003e只读成员\u003c/font\u003e、\u003cfont color=\"#d83931\"\u003e引用成员\u003c/font\u003e、\u003cfont color=\"#d83931\"\u003e对象成员\u003c/font\u003e需要在构造函数体前初始化。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"const"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 常量和 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"\u0026amp;"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 引用必须在定义时赋初值，故无法在构造函数体中赋值；类对象无法手动调用初始化函数，故需要在构造函数体前使用其初始化参数表进行初始化。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-qt935yp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-qt935yp","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"定义对象时，会自动调用构造函数进行初始化。初始化的顺序为类定义中声明的先后次序。若含有只读成员、引用成员、对象成员，除非定义时就初始化，否则一定要有构造函数。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-sqhdwem","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-sqhdwem","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.3 构造函数种类"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-3zyvg6a","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-3zyvg6a","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.3.1 默认构造函数"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-cs6ylev","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-cs6ylev","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在\u003cfont color=\"#4f81bd\"\u003e未定义任何特殊函数时\u003c/font\u003e（构造函数、赋值运算符、析构函数），编译器提供\u003cfont color=\"#4f81bd\"\u003e默认的构造函数\u003c/font\u003e："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-xf6k785","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-xf6k785","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-8hui0be","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-8hui0be","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-egl1mlk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-egl1mlk","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"无参构造函数：定义数据成员时给出了初值，会使用该函数完成初始化；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-er2jmbt","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-er2jmbt","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-97zax8h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-97zax8h","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"以有址引用为参数的构造函数：使用浅拷贝；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-fdd9wyj","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-fdd9wyj","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-ej94vbp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ej94vbp","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"以无址引用为参数的构造函数：对于类类型的成员，优先使用其移动构造函数，否则使用赋值构造函数；对于基本类型或指针，直接复制其值。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-3x3am3z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-3x3am3z","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"定义了构造函数后，则不再提供默认构造函数。如果仍然希望有默构造函数则使用 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"ClassName() = default;"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"、"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"ClassName(const ClassName \u0026amp;A) = default;"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"、"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"ClassName(ClassName \u0026amp;\u0026amp;A) = default;"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"同理，如果想要一定不使用默认构造函数，则使用关键字 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"delete"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-7cjo4oi","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-7cjo4oi","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.3.2 复制构造"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-1wb1gsr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-1wb1gsr","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"编译器也会提供默认的以对象 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"block-ref","TextMarkBlockRefID":"20260305082130-atkz9j7","TextMarkBlockRefSubtype":"s","TextMarkTextContent":"有址引用"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 为参数的构造函数，使用的是\u003cfont color=\"#d83931\"\u003e浅拷贝\u003c/font\u003e。即简单的将所有内容拷贝，例如，有指针指向体外空间时，简单的拷贝地址，导致两个对象的成员指针指向同一片地址。"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为实现\u003cfont color=\"#d83931\"\u003e深拷贝\u003c/font\u003e，需要自己编写以对象 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"block-ref","TextMarkBlockRefID":"20260305082130-atkz9j7","TextMarkBlockRefSubtype":"s","TextMarkTextContent":"有址引用"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 为参数的构造函数。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-wikvzo9","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-wikvzo9","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"ClassName(const ClassName \u0026a) {\n\t// 深拷贝\n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-yas58ii","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-yas58ii","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"加 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"block-ref","TextMarkBlockRefID":"20260305082130-n1jljn3","TextMarkBlockRefSubtype":"s","TextMarkTextContent":"const"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的原因：可以同时兼容\u003cfont color=\"#c0504d\"\u003e常量对象\u003c/font\u003e、\u003cfont color=\"#c0504d\"\u003e临时对象\u003c/font\u003e、普通对象的拷贝。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-e2bqu7y","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-e2bqu7y","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.3.3 移动构造"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-us88gey","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-us88gey","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"也会默认提供。指的是 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"block-ref","TextMarkBlockRefID":"20260305082130-atkz9j7","TextMarkBlockRefSubtype":"s","TextMarkTextContent":"无址引用"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（临时的、没有名称、不能取地址、只能出现在赋值运算符右侧的表达式的引用）为参数的构造函数。直接接管临时（局部）对象指针指向的空间，而不用进行拷贝。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-xoki181","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-xoki181","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"MyClass(MyClass\u0026\u0026 other) noexcept\n        : name(std::move(other.name)), p(other.p)\n    {\n\t\t   other.p = nullptr;\n        // ...\n    }µµ\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-yity3bz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-yity3bz","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对于指针，可以对其进行浅拷贝（复制内存地址），将原地址的所有权进行移动，即可完成窃取；对于简单类型，如 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"int"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ，直接进行复制是最高效的做法；而对于复杂类型，如 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"string"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，使用 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"std::move"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 进行窃取，否则会进行深拷贝。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-o45554k","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-o45554k","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2 析构函数"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-1n4gq8o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-1n4gq8o","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在一个对象 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"block-ref","TextMarkBlockRefID":"20260305082130-o62r477","TextMarkBlockRefSubtype":"s","TextMarkTextContent":"生命周期"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 结束时，会自动调用析构函数。析构函数可以释放指针成员指向的体外空间。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-4nzfkjh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-4nzfkjh","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"特点："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-3kltsxn","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-3kltsxn","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-rbaguzo","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-rbaguzo","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-pgkd9cx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-pgkd9cx","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"析构函数只能有一个，函数名为 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"~ClassName"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-ag9fkl5","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ag9fkl5","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-8uc8rv4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-8uc8rv4","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"无返回值，无参数；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-l3gtwof","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-l3gtwof","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-u3idorm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-u3idorm","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"可以手动调用。"}]}]}]}]}